                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding-right: 10px;"><img alt=""  src="/contentimages/arrow.gif" /></td>
                    <td>
                    <p>澳洲國家安全局 (Australian National Security): <a  onclick="ntptEventTag('ev=PartnerLead&PartnerId=nationalsecurity');" target="_blank" href="http://www.nationalsecurity.gov.au"><span style="color: #000000;">www.nationalsecurity.gov.au</span></a></p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding-right: 10px;"><img alt=""  src="/contentimages/arrow.gif" /></td>
                    <td>
                    <p>澳洲健康照護機構 (Medicare Australia): <a  onclick="ntptEventTag('ev=PartnerLead&PartnerId=medicareaustralia');" target="_blank" href="http://www.medicareaustralia.gov.au/public/migrants/visitors/index.jsp"><span style="color: #000000;">www.medicareaustralia.gov.au</span></a></p>
