                    <p>澳洲政府氣象局 (Australian Government Bureau of Meteorology): <a  onclick="ntptEventTag('ev=PartnerLead&PartnerId=bom');" target="_blank" href="http://www.bom.gov.au"><span style="color: #000000;">www.bom.gov.au</span></a></p>
